ESCO global skills layer
========================

esco/skills_en.csv is derived from the ESCO classification v1.1.1, published by
the European Commission.

  ESCO (European Skills, Competences, Qualifications and Occupations)
  (c) European Union, 2017-2024 — https://esco.ec.europa.eu/

Redistributed under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International licence
(CC BY 4.0): https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/
Obtained via the Tabiya Open Dataset (CC BY 4.0):
  https://github.com/tabiya-tech/tabiya-open-dataset

Modifications: only preferredLabel, altLabels and skillType are retained;
aliases shorter than 3 chars, purely numeric aliases, and a denylist of generic
terms were removed to reduce false positives. Source IDs reference
http://data.europa.eu/esco/skill/...
